---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="EU AI Act Conformity Assessment Implementation | AiLex Consulting" 
       description="Systematic conformity assessment implementation for EU AI Act compliance. Professional guidance through Article 43 requirements with comprehensive documentation frameworks.">

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50">
  <!-- Professional Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-blue-300 text-lg font-serif italic">SCIENTIA ET LEX</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          EU AI Act Conformity Assessment Implementation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Systematic implementation of Article 43 conformity assessment procedures through Claude AI-enhanced methodology achieving comprehensive regulatory compliance.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/emergency-assessment" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors text-center">
            Request Professional Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="#methodology" class="border border-slate-400 hover:border-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors text-center">
            Review Implementation Framework
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How Does Conformity Assessment Implementation Work? -->
  <section id="methodology" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800 mb-12 text-center">
        How Does EU AI Act Conformity Assessment Implementation Function?
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-slate-800 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold">01</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800">Assessment Framework Design</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Systematic analysis of AI system characteristics against EU AI Act requirements, establishing comprehensive assessment parameters aligned with Article 43 specifications and Annex VII documentation standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-blue-800 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold">02</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800">Technical Documentation Assembly</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Comprehensive documentation compilation covering risk management systems, quality management processes, and technical specifications required for conformity assessment procedures.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-800 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold">03</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800">Compliance Verification Process</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Detailed verification of conformity assessment procedures against regulatory requirements, ensuring systematic compliance with harmonised standards and technical specifications.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-red-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-red-800 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold">04</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800">Declaration Implementation</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Professional preparation and implementation of EU conformity declarations, CE marking procedures, and ongoing compliance monitoring frameworks for regulatory maintenance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Are the Key Conformity Assessment Deliverables? -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800 mb-12 text-center">
        What Are the Key Conformity Assessment Deliverables?
      </h2>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Technical Documentation Package</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Comprehensive Annex VII documentation including system specifications, risk assessments, and quality management procedures aligned with Article 43 requirements.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-800">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Conformity Assessment Report</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Detailed assessment analysis demonstrating compliance with harmonised standards and regulatory specifications for high-risk AI systems.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-800">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">EU Declaration of Conformity</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Formal declaration documentation with CE marking guidance and regulatory compliance certification for market placement.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-800">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Ongoing Compliance Framework</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Systematic monitoring procedures and compliance maintenance protocols ensuring continued regulatory adherence post-implementation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section for AEO -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800 mb-12 text-center">
        Conformity Assessment Implementation Requirements
      </h2>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
            What documentation is required for EU AI Act conformity assessment?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Conformity assessment requires comprehensive technical documentation under Annex VII, including detailed system descriptions, risk management documentation, quality management systems, and compliance monitoring procedures.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our systematic approach ensures complete documentation alignment with Article 43 requirements and harmonised standards for regulatory compliance.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
            How long does conformity assessment implementation typically require?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Standard conformity assessment implementation requires 4-6 weeks for comprehensive documentation and verification procedures, depending on AI system complexity and existing documentation quality.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Emergency assessments can be completed within 6 days through our Claude AI-enhanced methodology for urgent compliance requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
            Which AI systems require formal conformity assessment procedures?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            High-risk AI systems listed in Annex III require formal conformity assessment, including systems for critical infrastructure, education, employment, essential services, law enforcement, and administration of justice.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our assessment framework systematically determines conformity requirements based on AI system classification and intended use parameters.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Professional Consultation Interface -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">
          Professional Conformity Assessment Consultation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Systematic conformity assessment implementation through proven regulatory methodology. Professional consultation available for urgent compliance requirements.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-700 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">6 Days</div>
              <div class="text-slate-300">Emergency Assessment</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">99.7%</div>
              <div class="text-slate-300">Regulatory Coverage</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">Â£9,500</div>
              <div class="text-slate-300">Professional Service</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/emergency-assessment" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Schedule Assessment Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="border border-slate-400 hover:border-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Request Professional Guidance
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What documentation is required for EU AI Act conformity assessment?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Conformity assessment requires comprehensive technical documentation under Annex VII, including detailed system descriptions, risk management documentation, quality management systems, and compliance monitoring procedures."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question", 
      "name": "How long does conformity assessment implementation typically require?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Standard conformity assessment implementation requires 4-6 weeks for comprehensive documentation and verification procedures, depending on AI system complexity and existing documentation quality."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which AI systems require formal conformity assessment procedures?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "High-risk AI systems listed in Annex III require formal conformity assessment, including systems for critical infrastructure, education, employment, essential services, law enforcement, and administration of justice."
      }
    }
  ]
}
</script>

</Layout>